item.title: Where do i get object id's
item.dc:creator: @zoro35 zoro35
item.description:
@zoro35 wrote:

First off find the Coords you want them.

Right click the booth to get the ID. Then in client.java add it in you makeGlobalObject
One of my bank booths look like this

        makeGlobalObject(3625, 3526, 2213, -1, 10); // bankbooth
